  "texts": [
    "Using our protocol for padlock probe production from oligo pools, the cost of synthesis per gene scales sublinearly with the number of genes.",
    "Hence, oligo pricing will not hinder scaling the probe set to tens of thousands of transcripts.",
    "Moreover, DART-FISH does not need any specialized equipment for neither rolony generation nor decoding.",
    "The decoding process is relatively fast because it depends on the diffusion and hybridization of very short oligos and a strong signal can be obtained by 5-10 min of incubation with the fluorescent decoding probes at room temperature.",
    "Likewise, stripping and washing away the unbound decoding probes is straightforward and fast at room temperature."
  ],
